name: Jampacked
description:
Jampacked is a casual adventure platformer made during the 2020 Quarantine jam!

In the game you go on a journey and collect items based on interactions. 
We made it to be lighthearted and wholesome for these stressful times.
All the love and stay safe,
H&B

Made together with the wonderful https://fusionhs.itch.io/
Sound and Music from GameMaster Audio Pro Sound Collection V1.3
